SGGS MCP Retrieval Server
=========================

This repository contains MCP server code for multilingual retrieval over Sri
Guru Granth Sahib Ji data.

Data and Attribution
--------------------

The corpus workflow is built around BaniDB by Khalis Foundation:
https://github.com/KhalisFoundation/BaniDB

The generated data may include or derive from:
- Sri Guru Granth Sahib Ji text
- English translation attributed in the source workflow to Dr. Sant Singh Khalsa
- Punjabi teeka attributed in the source workflow to Prof. Sahib Singh
- Spanish translation attributed in the source workflow to SikhNet

The MIT license in this repository applies to the code and documentation only.
Before publishing generated JSONL, Chroma indexes, embeddings, or packaged data
bundles, verify the source licenses and redistribution permissions for every
corpus and translation source.
